            <c02 level="item" id="d1e239">
               <did>
                  <unittitle>
                     <persname>William Leete Stone Sr.</persname>to 
                  <persname>[George Lathrop]
                  Perkins</persname>
                  </unittitle>
                  <unitdate>1831 Aug 21</unitdate>
                  <physdesc>
                     <genreform>ALS,</genreform>
                     <extent>3 p.</extent>
                  </physdesc>
               </did>
               <scopecontent>
                  <p>[Discusses Iroquois Indians, whose history
                  interested Stone; speculates on the spelling of the
                  Chieftain's name, On-kos or Uncas; says that, after
                  meeting the English colonists, the chief was
                  sometimes called Paquim or Paquiam, as well as Unca;
                  tries to get Perkins' help, as Perkins seems to be an
                  authority on the subject.]</p>
               </scopecontent>
            </c02>
            <c02 level="item" id="d1e261">
               <did>
                  <unittitle>
                     <persname>William Leete Stone, Jr.</persname>to 
                  <persname>Benson John Lossing</persname>
                  </unittitle>
                  <unitdate>1877 Jan 16</unitdate>
                  <physdesc>
                     <genreform>ALS,</genreform>
                     <extent>1 p.</extent>
                  </physdesc>
               </did>
               <scopecontent>
                  <p>[Asks him to become one of his subscribers; says
                  he is convinced that he will enjoy the
                  publication.]</p>
               </scopecontent>
            </c02>
            <c02 level="item" id="d1e283">
               <did>
                  <unittitle>
                     <persname>William Leete Stone, Jr.</persname>to 
                  <persname>Benson John Lossing</persname>
                  </unittitle>
                  <unitdate>1877 Dec 4</unitdate>
                  <physdesc>
                     <genreform>Printed Postcard</genreform>
                  </physdesc>
               </did>
               <scopecontent>
                  <p>[In Stone's hand; asks him to remit $2.25, the
                  price of 
                  <bibref>Bargain</bibref>. ]</p>
               </scopecontent>
            </c02>
            <c02 level="item" id="d1e305">
               <did>
                  <unittitle>
